features: Heavy Duty Plastic Silverware: These are quite heavy duty plastic forks spoons as disposable utensils go. Their superior construction and design make them reliably strong. They won’t break easily under the strain of heavy food such as chicken and steak.

Easy Cleanup: Disposable spoons and forks always give you the ability to avoid washing dishes. Clear disposable utensils can be simply thrown away after use for great convenience. With this cutlery set, you’ll get a quicker and easier cleanup on dish duty after a big event.

Suitable for Most Food: This disposable silverware feature a clear transparent design, which can be easily match any types of decor, perfect for home dinners, parties, picnics, restaurants and more big events, with all kinds of food items like appetizers, main courses or desserts.

High Quality Material & Perfect Details: These plastic utensils are made of high quality clear heavy weight plastic, colorless and tasteless. Thanks to its smooth, rounded edges, these ergonomic plastic forks spoons provide a comfortable dining experience for everybody.

Over-Valued Pack of 200: The package of this plastic silverware set includes 100pcs plastic forks, 100pcs plastic spoons, making the set great for large gatherings and events. Ensuring you with enough quantity to accommodate all.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Probaly the Best
reviews.reviewText: These are incredibly durable for disposable utensils. They also are reasonably priced. They are slightly more durable than the Kirkland ones but slightly more expensive. They come in a good box that is easy to see the contents. Worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Forks and spoons
reviews.reviewText: Love that I could get just forks and spoons. Never use up the knives if they come in the pack. These came quickly and don’t break when using them. I’m very happy and would purchase these again. They are exactly as described.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This Cuttery is certainly better than most anything you would get from a fast food restaurant. It is not quite as strong as the best stuff you could buy at your local market, but it's close enough and the price is right

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No dishes in my house lol
reviews.reviewText: I love using plastic silverware and this is well worth it. Very sturdy and durable. My kids threw away half of my real silverware so it's plastic from here on out lol. This is my go to, I don't use the knives.

reviews.reviewText: I've used about 2/3 of the box by now, and I haven't had a single one break. They're not really meant to be reused, but I could wash them and reuse them if I wanted. It's a bulk amount in bulk packaging, but much cheaper than buying smaller packs from local stores.
